<p>Methvin's&nbsp;evolution is rooted in our commitment to offer only the most functional, flexible and easy to use Web-based estimating and bidding solution since 2002. Three years ago, we began an extensive redevelopment effort of methvin, to engineer the existing application using the latest Java technology.</p>
<p>In today&rsquo;s fast-paced, competitive bidding environment, successful companies need innovative tools for forecasting profit and quickly generating quality cost estimates and winning bids. Over 500 professionals from leading infrastructure companies throughout the U.S. and Canada New Zealand have chosen Methvin as their solution for winning more profitable bids.</p>
